            "type": "code",
            "content": "# Debian/Ubuntu - /etc/network/interfaces\nauto eth0\niface eth0 inet static\n    address 192.168.1.10\n    netmask 255.255.255.0\n    gateway 192.168.1.1\n    dns-nameservers 8.8.8.8 8.8.4.4\n\n# RedHat/CentOS - /etc/sysconfig/network-scripts/ifcfg-eth0\nDEVICE=eth0\nBOOTPROTO=static\nIPADDR=192.168.1.10\nNETMASK=255.255.255.0\nGATEWAY=192.168.1.1\nDNS1=8.8.8.8\nONBOOT=yes\n\n# DNS - /etc/resolv.conf\nnameserver 8.8.8.8\nnameserver 8.8.4.4\n\n# Hostname\nhostnamectl set-hostname nouveau-nom\ncat /etc/hostname"
